It can also display CVARS that are added when using the item with these exact 2 actions:
onSelfPrimaryActionEnd
onSelfSecondaryActionEnd

<triggered_effect trigger="onSelfPrimaryActionEnd" action="ModifyCVar" cvar="medicalRegHealthAmount" operation="add" value="14"/>

The "name" is the name of the cvar.

